{"tid":530679,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家應該戒絕寫粵語口語","createTime":"2018-01-16T04:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T04:50:26.000Z","uid":25643,"like":12,"dislike":397,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"c85e12b6e82f621fae5920152f9a7ac7ef229d75","tid":530679,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:14:18.000Z","msg":"如果我寫 今日食咗早餐,就一定畀老師話我錯 但點解周街廣告, 報刊雜誌, 網絡文章, 傾計whatsapp 大家都係寫粵語<br />\n冇人去畀個大交叉佢, 批鬥投訴佢? 文法又錯用字又錯喎.口語係口講嘛, 文字肯定係用書面語啦.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老師話係啱就一定係啱，你夠膽質疑老師同成個教育系統？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好同我拗呢啲情況唔係書面, 寫出黎漢字就係中文,就應該用正統書面語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你用書面語大家都明, 唔止香港人, 中國台灣馬來華人都明,方便大家交流<br />\n而唔係粵語入文呢啲得香港兩廣海外華人識嘅方言土語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且書面語同國語/普通話契合無縫, 書面語好就國語/普通話好, 唔駛溝埋啲香港俚語俗詞入正統中文<br />\n所以先推普教中嘛,書面語同普通話係絕配. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後再學啲大陸網絡用語 傻逼 醬紫 個啲, 打入中國人圈子冇難度<br />\n<br />\n我建議大家自己同朋友whatsapp ig 只用書面語, 就好似練習英文一樣練好正統中文<br />\n見到街有粵語字廣告, 報紙雜誌有粵文文章, 即刻打電話投訴<br />\n網上KOL youtube 有粵語字即刻unfollow<br />\n學語言一向係靠環境浸淫, 唔寫/睇多啲書面語, 正統中文程度點提升?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬DSE 都係考書面語, 你成日text 粵語俗字點考得好入大學搵好工賺大錢<br />\n有錢大把女屌, 而且書面語普通話好大把大陸妹台妹馬拉妹玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由今日起, 為自己為下一代締造無粵語污染嘅書面語環境<br />\n<br />\n<br />\np.s.<br />\n文言文個啲老屎忽嘢唔好提啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,冇人用又唔我手寫我口. 識書面語講普通話就好似我手寫我口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1919年五四運動之後北方話就係文字新正統，你鍾唔鍾意都要承認<br />\n中國只有一個，中文只有一種，對應嘅就係國語／普通話<br />\n除非你搞獨立，唔係粵語 粵文只係大一統歷史長河嘅沙石"},{"pid":"a4fb32f962332c724d91966b415550c112b0cc6c","tid":530679,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2039a25d0f1ef8042c48b3daeb18edad597551e","tid":530679,"uid":11484,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:18:01.000Z","msg":"樓豬又學人打口語？"},{"pid":"4aa219753e677574037d016371fa96af8b6d38a2","tid":530679,"uid":25643,"like":2,"dislike":80,"score":-78,"quote":{"pid":"f2039a25d0f1ef8042c48b3daeb18edad597551e","tid":530679,"uid":11484,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:18:01.000Z","msg":"樓豬又學人打口語？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"我都想打書面語﹐但中文差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寫篇嘢出嚟就係唔想大家好似我咁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906f1aec3fbcdf52589a896b0b613a80aef19140","tid":530679,"uid":121409,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:21:28.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到樓主用口語寫依篇垃圾即刻負皮左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b224a3738d57c36d935b0ecf62c3a04f85e483f7","tid":530679,"uid":25643,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"906f1aec3fbcdf52589a896b0b613a80aef19140","tid":530679,"uid":121409,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:21:28.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到樓主用口語寫依篇垃圾即刻負皮左<img src=\"/assets/faces/