s=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4478f666e15628feb32c38646cd4f16f3663eee9","tid":530679,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:07:39.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n我就係想搞獨立"},{"pid":"b37c0ef4594155d286d8f60127031a845e1e51ab","tid":530679,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:53:19.000Z","msg":"其實文言文係最優雅，可惜中學上堂只學識睇，學唔識寫"},{"pid":"afd5d421245d3460a554e458d79f1283a5701651","tid":530679,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"其實反中係反1949年之後既中華人民共和國囉"},{"pid":"bddafcf20aace954c4c12b44ab250d99a2eae621","tid":530679,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c85e12b6e82f621fae5920152f9a7ac7ef229d75","tid":530679,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:14:18.000Z","msg":"如果我寫 今日食咗早餐,就一定畀老師話我錯 但點解周街廣告, 報刊雜誌, 網絡文章, 傾計whatsapp 大家都係寫粵語<br />\n冇人去畀個大交叉佢, 批鬥投訴佢? 文法又錯用字又錯喎.口語係口講嘛, 文字肯定係用書面語啦.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老師話係啱就一定係啱，你夠膽質疑老師同成個教育系統？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好同我拗呢啲情況唔係書面, 寫出黎漢字就係中文,就應該用正統書面語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你用書面語大家都明, 唔止香港人, 中國台灣馬來華人都明,方便大家交流<br />\n而唔係粵語入文呢啲得香港兩廣海外華人識嘅方言土語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且書面語同國語/普通話契合無縫, 書面語好就國語/普通話好, 唔駛溝埋啲香港俚語俗詞入正統中文<br />\n所以先推普教中嘛,書面語同普通話係絕配. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後再學啲大陸網絡用語 傻逼 醬紫 個啲, 打入中國人圈子冇難度<br />\n<br />\n我建議大家自己同朋友whatsapp ig 只用書面語, 就好似練習英文一樣練好正統中文<br />\n見到街有粵語字廣告, 報紙雜誌有粵文文章, 即刻打電話投訴<br />\n網上KOL youtube 有粵語字即刻unfollow<br />\n學語言一向係靠環境浸淫, 唔寫/睇多啲書面語, 正統中文程度點提升?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬DSE 都係考書面語, 你成日text 粵語俗字點考得好入大學搵好工賺大錢<br />\n有錢大把女屌, 而且書面語普通話好大把大陸妹台妹馬拉妹玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由今日起, 為自己為下一代締造無粵語污染嘅書面語環境<br />\n<br />\n<br />\np.s.<br />\n文言文個啲老屎忽嘢唔好提啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,冇人用又唔我手寫我口. 識書面語講普通話就好似我手寫我口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1919年五四運動之後北方話就係文字新正統，你鍾唔鍾意都要承認<br />\n中國只有一個，中文只有一種，對應嘅就係國語／普通話<br />\n除非你搞獨立，唔係粵語 粵文只係大一統歷史長河嘅沙石"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:18:23.000Z","msg":"點解咁撚on9既人都可以有ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f21fc097a6b93b15f00a177ba9b49ff7a1c1ddd","tid":530679,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:30:22.000Z","msg":"以前高登雖然有真心膠但都唔會咁多ʅ（◞‿◟）ʃ"},{"pid":"390de0dd9d6dc9b15a0e5b5495ac8588af435240","tid":530679,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:46:47.000Z","msg":"關你撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26fbfe624a747239755ad8b50a3ad395cb7ead6","tid":530679,"uid":93450,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9f21fc097a6b93b15f00a177ba9b49ff7a1c1ddd","tid":530679,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:30:22.000Z","msg":"以前高登雖然有真心膠但都唔會咁多ʅ（◞‿◟）ʃ"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T17:39:25.000Z","msg":"三百幾個真心膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9616b1ca03a622963d29def18c541eccdcd44024","tid":530679,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7389fd6736b88f3883af33b88a411377